This template is used to create a row in the infobox with social media links. It is used in the {{tll|Infobox}} template.

This template relies on the Lua module: {{ll|Module:Socials}}.

{{Infobox
| title = Project
| class = theme-blue
| 
    {{Infobox/image
    | p1 = [[File:Image.png|link=]]
    }}
    {{Infobox/section
    | color = var(--color-blue)
    | id = 1
    | 1 = Links
    | 2 = 
        {{Infobox/socials
        | type=discord
        | link=https://discord.gg
        | Discord server
        }}
        {{Infobox/socials
        | type=steam
        | link=https://steamcommunity.com
        | Steam Workshop page
        }}
        {{Infobox/socials
        | type=github
        | link=https://github.com/
        | GitHub repository
        }}
        {{Infobox/socials
